FBIS4-21963 "jptot016__l94020" JPRS-TOT-94-016-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 14 April 1994 LATIN AMERICA PERU Peace Agreement With Shining Path Peace Agreement With Shining Path Fujimori Has Third Guzman Letter PY1404155494 Lima Global de Television Network in Spanish 0130 GMT 14 Apr 94 PY1404155494 Lima Global de Television Network Spanish BFN [Excerpt] President Alberto Fujimori announced today he has a third letter from Shining Path leader Abimael Guzman, and that he will reveal the letter at the appropriate time. Fujimori also denied that a letter published in a local magazine is real. [begin recording] Fujimori: [Words indistinct] second, I am keeping the third letter under lock, in a safe, and no one else knows the combination. I therefore don't see how the letter could have left my safe. Then [words indistinct] the magazine published a letter which is not the third letter. I deny it. [passage omitted]
